{
  "stem": "15721.2",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "We knew enough Jewish history to know the Jews had lived what we thought were under worse conditions, at least initially.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And secondly, we thought it couldn't last anyhow.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "How would the world stand for this kind of a government, for this kind of a movement to come to power?",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It's the first time in history that a movement came to power who had as one of its major planks the elimination of Jews, at least from their realm.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because that was certainly what they decided in the early years of their rule.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I had one personal encounter with-- with a-- with Hitler, if you-- I'd call it that.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "My school friend and I decided one time to go towards town and there was a-- a little restaurant that served tea and cookies and the like.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It was only a tea-- tea room.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And he, in particular, liked it, had been there are a number of times and said after school one day, why don't we go there and have a glass-- cup tea, a glass tea with each other?",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I thought it was a wonderful idea.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And so we went down there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was maybe a half hour walk from school.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we were sitting there and I had just begun to drink my tea when the door flew open and six or eight very burly SA men in uniform came in, lined up, looked at the room, nodded, and in walked Hitler was sat down at one of the tables to have a glass of tea.",
      "word_count": 56
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I have to tell you, I didn't stay.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I told my friend, who was the tallest in the class and-- and the exemplar of Nordic view-- appearance.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I said, Albert, you pay.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I'm leaving.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I sneaked out along the wall.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
